  "title": "Garland Maker",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Create traditional and custom floral garlands based on client needs.</li><li>Able to manage the orders and team.</li><li>Select and prepare flowers, leaves, and other materials</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and freshness of floral materials</li><li>Work efficiently to meet deadlines, especially during peak seasons and events</li><li>Collaborate with the decoration team for large-scale projects</li><li>Assist in packaging and transporting finished products, if required</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Experience in making flower garlands (traditional or modern styles)</li><li>Good hand-eye coordination and attention to detail</li><li>Knowledge of flower types, freshness, and handling</li><li>Creative flair and interest in decorative arts</li><li>Ability to work independently and under time pressure</li><li>Punctual, reliable, and customer-focused</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>5.5 workdays</li><li>Able to work in weekends and public holidays, if required</li><li>Able to converse in english</li><li>Able to work in shifts</li><li>1or 2 years expirence in related field is required</li></ul>",
